								</svg>
								<div>
									<strong>Transformer:</strong> Converts high voltage to low voltage for the control circuit
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-accent mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0"
